      "content": "\"strangely beautiful\" feels like such a coping mechanism. it doesn't change the fact that it's all just noise. i'm tired of the noise. i feel like i'm just waiting for something to finally end so i don't have to keep performing this \"meaningful\" life anymore. it just feels like a heavy weight i didn't ask to carry.",
